text: 10:25 Mat 9:34; 12:24; Mrk 3:22; Luk 11:15  Tung-inbasingna makhoigi ojagum amasung manaina makhoigi mapugum oirakpa aduna okle. Aduga yumgi yumburen aduda Beelzebul10:25 Lai phattabasinggi makok Satan-gi atoppa maming ama. haina makhoina kourabadi, mahakki imunggi misingdadi kayada henna thina kougadaba!
